									<p class="technologies__desc">Since we want our products to remain relevant for as long as possible, we implement the most up-to-date technologies. To ensure high-quality streaming video, we use all the advantages of WebRTC technology. In addition, artificial intelligence (AI) is used to analyze video meetings more thoroughly. Integration with Amazon and Google products, such as AWS S3, AWS CloudFront, AWS Lambda, Firebase, helps to expand the capabilities of our white-label software.</p>
